data.body:
When you launch chrome in debug mode, it opens a new tab but vcode attaches to soon to the already opened tab that can be any website. It should attach to the tab it created instead. Or look for the url in current tabs before opening a new one.

``` json
{
    "version": "0.10.6",
    "configurations": [
        {
            "name": "Launch chrome",
            "type": "chrome",
            "request": "launch",
            "url": "http://localhost:8080/",
            "webRoot": "default",
            "sourceMaps": true
        }
    ]
}
```
